<L>__{ext welles' house. pool day}
<A>__{welles, wrapped in a bathrobe, is pacing quickly around the perimeter of his backyard pool. he is puffing on a cigar and grunting to himself as he scribbles down notes. mank, wearing sunglasses and a battered fedora and looking decidedly hung over, comes from the house to the pool. welles roars up to him:}
<C>__{welles}
