<D>__{howard hughes, he would just kill us. hearst he would kill us and fuck everything we ever loved.}
<C>__{welles}
<D>__{we're doing hearst.}
<A>__{a beat. mank slowly removes his sunglasses and leans forward, dead serious. a beat.}
<C>__{mank}
<D>__{you may think you know what you're talking about, kid, but believe me, you don't. you're talking about going into a battle you can never win on a battlefield so far above things like movies and hollywood that hearst won't even have to glance down when he crushes you. when he flicks you away with one finger. i'm talking about money and influence and evil beyond your capacity to imagine hell.}
