<D>__{how does it feel, mank? going up to the palace and making all the lords and ladies laugh as you tell your little stories and beg for crumbs at the table? how does it feel being the ugly little monkey they keep to amuse themselves ?!}
<A>__{mank leaps to his feet}
<C>__{mank}
